# 3. 01 Matrix

01 Matrix

## Logic

For every `1`, find nearest `0`.

### Sources

All `0`s

### BFS Meaning

Distance from nearest zero

---

# Pattern

```python id="jlwm71"
Put all 0s into queue

BFS:
    update distance of 1s
```

