# 5. Nearest Exit in Maze

Nearest Exit from Entrance in Maze

## Logic

Shortest path from entrance to boundary.

### Source

Single entrance

### BFS Meaning

Shortest steps

This is normal BFS, not multi-source.

---

# Pattern

```python id="3gjlwm"
Start from entrance

BFS level by level

First boundary reached = answer
```

