# 6. Fire Spread Problems

Common grid pattern.

## Logic

Fire spreads each minute.

### Sources

All fire cells

### BFS Meaning

Time taken to spread

---

# How to identify Multi Source BFS

Whenever problem says:

* nearest
* minimum distance
* spread
* infection
* time to reach
* all simultaneously
* closest source

Think:

# Multi Source BFS

---

# Golden Rule

If many starting points affect grid simultaneously:

```python id="jlwm5w"
Push all of them into queue first
```

THAT is Multi Source BFS.
